We picked the best date.

19
00:02:53,506 --> 00:03:00,002
There's a solar eclipse today
and it will be clear.

20
00:03:00,146 --> 00:03:05,413
ln some cultures,
solar eclipses are considered lucky.

21
00:03:07,353 --> 00:03:11,221
- Really?
- Yes. Come on.

22
00:03:13,293 --> 00:03:17,627
- Mom, l'm nervous.
- Don't be such a baby.

23
00:03:18,331 --> 00:03:22,495
lt's the nicest day
for a beach wedding.

24
00:03:23,603 --> 00:03:26,037
Come, hug Mama.

25
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,465
