Yes or no?

494
00:40:11,208 --> 00:40:13,642
- Yes or no?
- Yes!

495
00:40:16,714 --> 00:40:19,308
l rest my case. Excuse me.

496
00:40:25,489 --> 00:40:28,083
l'm so smart!

497
00:40:38,235 --> 00:40:41,033
There! This is it.

498
00:41:13,537 --> 00:41:16,734
Miss Stephanie, it's Alfie, are you ready
to have your makeup done?

499
00:41:18,142 --> 00:41:21,669
Appear, appear, appear!
No need for makeup here!

500
00:41:21,745 --> 00:41:28,651
Just a spritz here and there,
throw your eyebrows in the air!

501
00:41:29,253 --> 00:41:31,221
Why are you dressed like that?

502
00:41:31,288 --> 00:41:34,746
Why? Are you mesmerized
by my gorgeousness?

503
00:41:34,825 --> 00:41:39,228
You're envious aren't you?
l have achieved perfection.

504
00:41:40,064 --> 00:41:41,793
Here, help me with this.

505
00:41:42,666 --> 00:41:46,625
Careful with the hair.
The hair is top priority.

506
00:41:49,306 --> 00:41:50,864
Where are you going?

507
00:41:50,941 --> 00:41:53,171
To the beach, where the boys are.

508
00:41:53,244 --> 00:41:54,609
But we're running late...

509
00:41:54,678 --> 00:41:56,976
Never mind that.
What about your makeup?

510
00:41:57,214 --> 00:41:59,205
Go! There!

511
00:41:59,783 --> 00:42:00,579
Stephanie?

512
00:42:01,418 --> 00:42:02,612
Stephanie, child.

513
00:42:03,954 --> 00:42:08,914
This is insane. A blast from the past.

514
00:42:10,494 --> 00:42:12,553
Stephanie, is that you?

515
00:42:12,630 --> 00:42:16,760
Uh... yeah.

516
00:42:19,036 --> 00:42:24,770
This is your Grandpa Bien.
Harold's grandfather.

517
00:42:24,842 --> 00:42:26,104
Oh?

518
00:42:28,245 --> 00:42:32,773
l know this is hard to believe,
but you must listen to me.

519
00:42:33,584 --> 00:42:39,352
l don't know how l ended up
in this body. l'm confused.

520
00:42:40,457 --> 00:42:42,152
Okay.

521
00:42:42,826 --> 00:42:44,293
Can you help me?

522
00:42:46,397 --> 00:42:49,230
Of course. We'll discuss it. Here.

523
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:52,492
- Where?
- We'll talk. Here.

524
00:42:53,971 --> 00:43:02,174
Here. Yes.
There.

525
00:43:04,248 --> 00:43:06,808
Blasted pest!
lnterfering with my plans.

526
00:43:08,352 --> 00:43:12,413
Where have you been?
We have so many clients to do.

527
00:43:13,190 --> 00:43:16,717
Were you picking up boys on the beach?
You have a job to do.

528
00:43:16,794 --> 00:43:21,128
- Toffee, do me first.
- Excuse me, l got here first.

529
00:43:23,601 --> 00:43:27,196
Excuse me,
l'm the maid of honor and l go first.

530
00:43:33,243 --> 00:43:37,976
Where are you going?
Do the bridesmaids.

531
00:44:03,607 --> 00:44:11,309
- What's up, boys? Got a drink for me?
- Come on, guys, a drink for Stef.

532
00:44:13,017 --> 00:44:14,450
Quick!

533
00:44:20,391 --> 00:44:23,758
Why don't we dance? Let's party.

534
00:44:29,233 --> 00:44:30,860
Party!

535
00:44:33,203 --> 00:44:38,835
That's what l like!
We're on the beach, we're so happy.

536
00:44:56,560 --> 00:44:59,996
So. Are you my first victim?

537
00:45:00,064 --> 00:45:03,329
Yes. And hopefully your last.

538
00:45:03,400 --> 00:45:09,635
Those are fighting words.
l may bite you.

539
00:45:10,541 --> 00:45:16,070
Just say ''Yes, l do''
and l'm yours forever.

540
00:45:17,047 --> 00:45:24,920
Oh my god. Forever is a dangerous word.
Won't you get tired of me?

541
00:45:24,988 --> 00:45:28,890
Me get tired of you? lmpossible.

542
00:45:30,894 --> 00:45:36,264
So where to? Your place or mine?

543
00:45:36,366 --> 00:45:39,733
Are you serious? Now?

544
00:45:39,803 --> 00:45:45,708
Yes. Life is short. And you are so hot.

545
00:45:46,310 --> 00:45:51,441
Then again, that's where
we're headed. Why wait.

546
00:45:51,915 --> 00:45:54,975
Let's go!
We can have seconds and thirds.

547
00:45:57,788 --> 00:45:59,585
Hi.

548
00:46:00,424 --> 00:46:01,584
Hello, child.

549
00:46:01,759 --> 00:46:04,660
l'd like a fresh look.

550
00:46:06,530 --> 00:46:07,622
Fresh?

551
00:46:07,698 --> 00:46:11,657
The no makeup look. You know.

552
00:46:13,837 --> 00:46:15,361
Alright, let's try that.

553
00:46:15,439 --> 00:46:21,639
But highlights on the cheekbones
and nose, and a bit of blusher. Thanks.

554
00:46:40,297 --> 00:46:41,628
Here.

555
00:46:42,032 --> 00:46:50,462
- Look at that. What a hunk.
- What are you doing, Stef?

556
00:46:50,541 --> 00:46:57,674
- You're making me crazy.
- Stef, what are you doing?

557
00:46:59,249 --> 00:47:03,686
Delicious.

558
00:47:07,724 --> 00:47:11,455
Babe, Stef, are you sure
you want to do this?

559
00:47:11,528 --> 00:47:13,120
Yes! Absolutely!

560
00:47:13,197 --> 00:47:15,893
- ls that your final answer?
- Yes, is that your final question?

561
00:47:15,966 --> 00:47:18,264
Stef.

562
00:47:18,769 --> 00:47:22,500
- Come on, let's go.
- Stef, this isn't right.

563
00:47:22,573 --> 00:47:25,474
What do you mean it's not right?
Don't be so fussy.

564
00:47:25,542 --> 00:47:28,170
- Stef.
- l need to make my quota, hurry.

565
00:47:28,245 --> 00:47:30,475
But didn't you say you wanted
our first time to be special?

566
00:47:30,647 --> 00:47:34,583
What! l said no such thing! Come on!

567
00:47:34,651 --> 00:47:37,017
Stef, we held back for 4 years.

568
00:47:37,821 --> 00:47:40,483
4 years? l refrained for 4 years?

569
00:47:40,657 --> 00:47:43,057
Let's not break our oath now.

570
00:47:43,160 --> 00:47:46,687
What oath?
l have not signed any contract.

571
00:47:46,763 --> 00:47:48,993
We made a pact, Stef.

572
00:47:49,733 --> 00:47:52,793
We would do this the right way.
We would wait until we were married.

573
00:47:53,170 --> 00:47:55,604
Married? Us?

574
00:47:55,672 --> 00:48:01,110
Yes, us.
You, me, here, later.

575
00:48:02,045 --> 00:48:06,573
Later? Here? You, me? Us?

576
00:48:07,417 --> 00:48:11,979
My wife is so cute.
You never fail to surprise me.

577
00:48:12,856 --> 00:48:18,294
l promise to take care of you,
to cherish you forever...

578
00:48:18,829 --> 00:48:22,026
to make you happy
every single moment of your life.

579
00:48:23,000 --> 00:48:24,262
l love you.

580
00:48:31,742 --> 00:48:33,505
Such things exist?

581
00:48:35,779 --> 00:48:39,943
Besides, it's just a few hours.
When the sun sets, we're legal.

582
00:48:40,617 --> 00:48:41,845
See you later, Babe.

583
00:48:41,919 --> 00:48:46,015
l'll be getting ready. You too, okay?

584
00:48:47,224 --> 00:48:49,249
Catch you later, wifey.

585
00:48:55,098 --> 00:49:02,231
l'm so fabulous! My God!

586
00:49:03,240 --> 00:49:04,172
There.

587
00:49:11,448 --> 00:49:14,383
What have you done? You jerk!

588
00:49:15,919 --> 00:49:20,117
My apologies!
l didn't know what l was doing.

589
00:49:20,190 --> 00:49:22,351
lsn't that the fashion today?

590
00:49:22,426 --> 00:49:24,189
You look like a mascot.

591
00:49:24,294 --> 00:49:26,728
This is a wedding,
not a children's party.

592
00:49:26,797 --> 00:49:29,527
You didn't become beautiful,
you just got colorful.

593
00:49:29,733 --> 00:49:31,701
You look like a fool.

594
00:49:38,108 --> 00:49:43,910
You nitwit! What have you done!

595
00:49:48,919 --> 00:49:49,749
Sit down!

596
00:49:52,823 --> 00:49:54,381
Wait for me, lady.

597
00:50:01,598 --> 00:50:03,998
Stop! Come back here!

598
00:50:18,715 --> 00:50:22,583
Miss, where are you going?
You can't leave.

599
00:50:22,652 --> 00:50:28,818
Nurse, l have a wedding to catch.
My very own. Can't you understand?

600
00:50:29,760 --> 00:50:31,455
Man, she's really stoned.

601
00:50:32,729 --> 00:50:33,991
l heard she's super-smart...

602
00:50:34,131 --> 00:50:37,567
that's how she lost her mind.
Poor thing.

603
00:50:37,634 --> 00:50:42,196
Why am l in a straitjacket?
lsn't this for crazy people?

604
00:50:42,272 --> 00:50:48,302
Do l look like a crazy person?
Tell me.

605
00:50:48,378 --> 00:50:52,906
The doctor says
you're a threat to human life.

606
00:50:52,983 --> 00:50:55,042
To yourself and others.

607
00:50:55,118 --> 00:50:59,077
Believe me, l'm not crazy.

608
00:50:59,823 --> 00:51:08,322
You can't lock me up,
l'm getting married!

609
00:51:11,101 --> 00:51:14,502
Dad, here's the check for the resort
and for the wedding package.

610
00:51:19,042 --> 00:51:22,637
1 .5 million pesos?
This is the price of a condo!

611
00:51:22,746 --> 00:51:25,613
l am not talking to you.

612
00:51:26,416 --> 00:51:34,187
Dad, this includes all expenses,
including guest lodgings. Sign it, Dad.

613
00:51:34,558 --> 00:51:39,222
lt's the wedding of Harold,
your first grandchild.

614
00:51:39,329 --> 00:51:41,763
Dad, don't tell me you're signing that.
